<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Shinzi Music - Web Player</title>
    <style>
        /* Base Styling */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #000000;
            color: #ffffff;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* Top Navigation Header (Mobile Friendly) */
        header {
            background-color: #121212;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #1db954; /* Spotify Green */
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .profile-icon {
            width: 35px;
            height: 35px;
            background-color: #535353;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Main Content Area */
        main {
            flex: 1;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #1e3264 0%, #121212 100%);
            padding: 20px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            padding-bottom: 90px; /* Space for the bottom player */
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        /* Playlist Grid */
        .grid-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); /* 2 columns for phone screens */
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: #181818;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .card:hover {
            background-color: #282828;
        }

        .card-img {
            width: 100%;
            aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
            background-color: #333;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 40px;
        }

        .card h3 {
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
        }

        .card p {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #b3b3b3;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        /* Bottom Music Player */
        .player {
            background-color: #181818;
            border-top: 1px solid #282828;
            height: 80px;
            width: 100%;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 0 15px;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .track-info {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .track-art {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            background-color: #1db954;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .track-text h4 {
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 3px;
        }

        .track-text p {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #b3b3b3;
        }

        .controls {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .play-btn {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: #000;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="logo">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" height="28" fill="currentColor">
                <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 14.5v-9l6 4.5-6 4.5z"/>
            </svg>
            Shinzi Music
        </div>
        <div class="profile-icon">S</div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <h2>Good Afternoon</h2>
        
        <div class="grid-container">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-img" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF7E5F, #FEB47B);">🔥</div>
                <h3>Top Hits India</h3>
                <p>Catch the hottest tracks right now.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-img" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00C9FF, #92FE9D);">🎧</div>
                <h3>Lofi Study Beats</h3>
                <p>Chill beats to focus and relax to.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-img" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8E2DE2, #4A00E0);">🌌</div>
                <h3>Midnight Vibes</h3>
                <p>Deep sounds for late night coding.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-img" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f12711, #f5af19);">🎸</div>
                <h3>Rock Classics</h3>
                <p>The legends of rock in one place.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Made for You</h2>
        <div class="grid-container">
             <div class="card">
                <div class="card-img" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #11998e, #38ef7d);">🎵</div>
                <h3>Daily Mix 1</h3>
                <p>A mix of music you love.</p>
            </div>
             <div class="card">
                <div class="card-img" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fc4a1a, #f7b733);">🔊</div>
                <h3>Discover Weekly</h3>
                <p>New music tailored for you.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <div class="player">
        <div class="track-info">
            <div class="track-art"></div>
            <div class="track-text">
                <h4>Not Playing</h4>
                <p>Shinzi AI</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="controls">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="#b3b3b3">
                <path d="M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z"/>
            </svg>
            <div class="play-btn">▶</div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
